RecyclerViewItemHolder.getInstance().childViews.add(holder.cardView);
}
```
Then, I accessed the ArrayList from the afterTextChanged method of the TextWatcher I set to the EditText. I used a for loop to check if the name of the cardView contains the search query, and applied View.GONE if it didn&#39;t.
```Java
private void initListeners() {
